Features

column26:
this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. The side air mesh pockets of this backpack are where you can keep your water bottle or other small accessories. Ensuring that you are relaxed while discovering a new place are the padded shoulder straps and back which provide you with a comfortable carrying experience. For the load management this backpack has been furnished with compression straps at the top and bottom. You can slip in some snacks or accessories in the front flat zippered mesh pocket of this Wildcraft Pack Y 28 L Backpack. This bag has specially designed channels on the back which facilitate a sufficient flow of air. As this backpack is bar tacked on specialised machines it is robust and sure to last you for a longer time.\xa0Keeping all your possessions safely encased within are the zipper and buckle closure of this bag.

Features

As this backpack is equipped with one compartment and four pockets
column23:
you can arrange your belongings in order of use. Keeping you comfortable while you are cycling are the padded shoulders and back of this bag. You can slip your music player and other gadgets into the internal zippered pocket of this Wildcraft Hydrator 7 L Backpack. When you want to hang this bag onto the cycle handle you can use the reinforced haul loop. Ensuring that you don\u2019t have to stop every time you want a drink of water is are the bladder pouch and 2 litre hydration bladder of this backpack. The side air mesh pocket is where you can keep some accessories which you would want to reach quickly. You can keep some snacks to munch on in the front flat pocket of this compact bag. This bag is going to accompany you on multiple occasions as it is bar tacked on specialised machines. Keeping all your possessions safely encased within are the buckle and zipper closure of this well-equipped backpack.
